  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lore</h2>You are completely desperate in life, on your shoulders hung too much debt and you fear for your future, in front of your eyes flashes all the horror of what you will have to go through, but suddenly you come across an ad for a game in which you can win a lot of money, this more than covers your debts. Are you willing to put your life on the line to walk away with pockets full of money?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/69959b464f6a911780b0bcd8f32ba193.poster.avif?t=1716135444\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/69959b464f6a911780b0bcd8f32ba193.webm?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/69959b464f6a911780b0bcd8f32ba193.mp4?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactics and Strategy</h2>Outsmart your opponents and leave the tavern as the last survivor, what bullet will you get this time? A blank or a...<br>Let's find out, pull the trigger, set an example for the rest of the table. After all, the victory looks so tempting, just a little bit left and the money is yours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/763dc1b391882fa523c8ad5779f6a48d.poster.avif?t=1716135444\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/763dc1b391882fa523c8ad5779f6a48d.webm?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/763dc1b391882fa523c8ad5779f6a48d.mp4?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items</h2>Get various bonuses for your courage and determination. Who knows, maybe thanks to this very thing, you can turn the game in your favor, quickly make a choice, otherwise someone will take advantage of your doubts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/9033a67db3ea6486305138b57cc44e5e.poster.avif?t=1716135444\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/9033a67db3ea6486305138b57cc44e5e.webm?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/9033a67db3ea6486305138b57cc44e5e.mp4?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2>Stand out among the rest, change the image of your character, pick up your style that will reflect you at the round table of the chosen ones.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/1e809618374477d9fe819cfd47275d75.poster.avif?t=1716135444\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/1e809618374477d9fe819cfd47275d75.webm?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841990/extras/1e809618374477d9fe819cfd47275d75.mp4?t=1716135444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
